[
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "1",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054001",
        "Body":  "The hour (of Judgment) is nigh and the moon is cleft asunder.\n\t\t\t\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5127\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5128\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "10",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054010",
        "Body":  "Then he called on his Lord: \"I am one overcome: do thou then help\n\t\t\t(me)!\" \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5136\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "11",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054011",
        "Body":  "So We opened the gates of heaven with water pouring forth."
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "12",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054012",
        "Body":  "And We caused the earth to gush forth with springs so the waters\n\t\t\tmet (and rose) to the extent decreed. \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5137\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "13",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054013",
        "Body":  "But We bore him on an (Ark) made of broad planks and caulked with\n\t\t\tpalm-fibre: \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5138\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "14",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054014",
        "Body":  "She floats under Our eyes (and care): a recompense to one who had\n\t\t\tbeen rejected (with scorn)! \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5139\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "15",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054015",
        "Body":  "And We have left this as a Sign (for all time): then is there any\n\t\t\tthat will receive admonition? \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5140\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5141\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "16",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054016",
        "Body":  "But how (terrible) was My Penalty and My Warning? \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5142\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "17",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054017",
        "Body":  "And We have indeed made the Qur\u0027an easy to understand and\n\t\t\tremember: then is there any that will receive admonition?\n\t\t\t\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5143\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "18",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054018",
        "Body":  "The `Ad (people) (too) rejected (Truth): then how terrible was my\n\t\t\tPenalty and my Warning!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "19",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054019",
        "Body":  "For We sent against them a furious wind on a Day of violent\n\t\t\tDisaster \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5144\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "2",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054002",
        "Body":  "But if they see a Sign they turn away and say \"This is (but)\n\t\t\ttransient magic.\" \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5129\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "20",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054020",
        "Body":  "Plucking out men as if they were roots of palm-trees torn up\n\t\t\t(from the ground)."
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "21",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054021",
        "Body":  "Yea how (terrible) was my Penalty and my Warning! \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5145\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "22",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054022",
        "Body":  "But We have indeed made the Qur\u0027an easy to understand and\n\t\t\tremember: then is there any that will receive admonition?"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "23",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054023",
        "Body":  "The Thamud (also) rejected (their) Warners."
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "24",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054024",
        "Body":  "For they said: \"what! a man! a solitary one from among ourselves!\n\t\t\tshall we follow such a one? Truly should we then be straying in\n\t\t\tmind and mad! \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5146\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5147\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "25",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054025",
        "Body":  "\"Is it that the Message is sent to him of all people amongst us?\n\t\t\tNay he is a liar an insolent one!\" \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5148\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "26",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054026",
        "Body":  "Ah! they will know on the morrow which is the liar the insolent\n\t\t\tone!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "27",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054027",
        "Body":  "For We will send the she camel by way of trial for them.  So\n\t\t\twatch them (O Saleh) and possess thyself in patience!\n\t\t\t\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5149\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "28",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054028",
        "Body":  "And tell them that the water is to be divided between them: each\n\t\t\tone\u0027s right to drink being brought forward (by suitable turns).\n\t\t\t\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5150\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "29",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054029",
        "Body":  "But they called to their companion and he took a sword in hand\n\t\t\tand hamstrung (her)."
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "3",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054003",
        "Body":  "They reject (the warning) and follow their (own) lusts but every\n\t\t\tmatter has its appointed time. \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5130\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "30",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054030",
        "Body":  "Ah! how (terrible) was My Penalty and My Warning!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "31",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054031",
        "Body":  "For We sent against them a single Mighty Blast and they became\n\t\t\tlike the dry stubble used by one who pens cattle. \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5151\u003c/span\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5152\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "32",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054032",
        "Body":  "And We have indeed made the Qur\u0027an easy to understand and\n\t\t\tremember: then is there any that will receive admonition?"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "33",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054033",
        "Body":  "The People of Lut rejected (his) Warning. \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5153\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "34",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054034",
        "Body":  "We sent against them a violent tornado with showers of stones\n\t\t\t(which destroyed them) except Lut\u0027s household: them We delivered\n\t\t\tby early Dawn \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5154\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "35",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054035",
        "Body":  "As a Grace from Us: Thus do We reward those who give thanks.\n\t\t\t\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5155\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "36",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054036",
        "Body":  "And (Lut) did warn them of Our Punishment but they disputed about\n\t\t\tthe Warning. \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5156\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "37",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054037",
        "Body":  "And they even sought to snatch away his guests from him but We\n\t\t\tblinded their eyes.  (They heard:) \"now taste ye My Wrath and My\n\t\t\tWarning.\" \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5157\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "38",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054038",
        "Body":  "Early on the morrow an abiding Punishment seized them:"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "39",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054039",
        "Body":  "\"So taste ye My Wrath and My Warning.\""
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "4",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054004",
        "Body":  "There have already come to them Recitals wherein there is\n\t\t\t(enough) to check (them) \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5131\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "40",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054040",
        "Body":  "And We have indeed made the Qur\u0027an easy to understand and\n\t\t\tremember: then is there any that will receive admonition?"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "41",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054041",
        "Body":  "To the people of Pharaoh too aforetime came Warners (from Allah).\n\t\t\t\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5158\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "42",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054042",
        "Body":  "The (people) rejected all Our Signs; but We seized them with such\n\t\t\tPenalty (as comes) from One Exalted in Power able to carry out\n\t\t\tHis Will."
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "43",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054043",
        "Body":  "Are your Unbelievers (O Quraish) better than they? or have ye an\n\t\t\timmunity in the Sacred Books? \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5159\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "44",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054044",
        "Body":  "Or do they say: \"We acting together can defend ourselves\"?"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "45",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054045",
        "Body":  "Soon will their multitude be put to flight and they will show\n\t\t\ttheir backs."
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "46",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054046",
        "Body":  "Nay the Hour (of Judgment) is the time promised them (for their\n\t\t\tfull recompense): And that Hour will be Most grievous and most\n\t\t\tbitter. \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5160\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "47",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054047",
        "Body":  "Truly those in sin are the ones straying in mind and mad.\n\t\t\t\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5161\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "48",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054048",
        "Body":  "The day they will be dragged through the Fire on their faces\n\t\t\t(they will hear:) \"Taste ye the touch of Hell!\" \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5162\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "49",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054049",
        "Body":  "Verily all things have We created in proportion and measure.\n\t\t\t\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5163\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "5",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054005",
        "Body":  "Mature wisdom but (the preaching of) Warners profits them not."
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "50",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054050",
        "Body":  "And Our command is but a single (Act) like the twinkling of an\n\t\t\teye. \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5164\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "51",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054051",
        "Body":  "And (oft) in the past have We destroyed gangs like unto you: Then\n\t\t\tis there any that will receive admonition? \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5165\u003c/span\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5166\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "52",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054052",
        "Body":  "All that they do is noted in (their) Books (of Deeds):\n\t\t\t\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5167\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "53",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054053",
        "Body":  "Every matter small and great is on record."
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "54",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054054",
        "Body":  "As to the Righteous they will be in the midst of Gardens and\n\t\t\tRivers. \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5168\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "55",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054055",
        "Body":  "In an Assembly of Truth in the Presence of a Sovereign\n\t\t\tOmnipotent. \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5169\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5170\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5171\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "6",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054006",
        "Body":  "Therefore (O Prophet) turn away from them.  The day that the\n\t\t\tCaller will call (them) to a terrible affair. \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5132\u003c/span\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5133\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "7",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054007",
        "Body":  "They will come forth  their eyes humbled from (their) graves\n\t\t\t(torpid) like locusts scattered abroad \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5134\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "8",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054008",
        "Body":  "Hastening with eyes transfixed towards the Caller! \"Hard is this\n\t\t\tDay!\" the Unbelievers will say."
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "YAT",
        "SurahNumber":  "54",
        "AyahNumber":  "9",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/054009",
        "Body":  "Before them the People of Noah rejected (their apostle): they\n\t\t\trejected Our servant and said \"Here is one possessed!\" and he was\n\t\t\tdriven out. \u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5135\u003c/span\u003e"
    }
]
